#summary Getting Started page.

= Getting Started =

SkyQuant AFL file applying launch ephemeris building. Once calculated ephemeris load to a memory for fast use in work. It lives till AmiBroker closing. Building processing steps can be observed in _Log -> Trace_ window.

https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-EM2lSOETwbo/T1Mmvrp5uLI/AAAAAAAAADw/qqz00z4FIV8/s993/trace.png

Each object has it's own identification number. These IDs must be used in planets list composing in opened indicator's Properties window.

https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-zQEgBJgX3_s/T1RxetgjTsI/AAAAAAAAAD8/Q_HdJDduvss/s392/prop.jpg
